<HEADLINE>
<P>
CLINTON DEFENDERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Regarding Whitewater: The question of innocence or guilt is still 
unanswered. But the person who says, "Who cares what the Clintons did back in 
the '80s?" is desperately unwise. 
</P>
<P>
 DAVID R. HUGHES 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles 
</P>
