<P>
 Sixth-ranked Villa Park relied on its doubles teams in a 13-8 victory over No. 
9 Canyon in a Century League boys' tennis match Tuesday at Villa Park High. 
</P>
<P>
 "Doubles are our weakness," Villa Park Coach Dave Colville said before the 
match."We should win our singles 9-0, so we need a few wins from our doubles." 
</P>
<P>
