Laussade, who won, 6-4, 6-4, to give Villa Park (11-2, 4-1 in league) an 8 
2/3-5 1/3 lead at the end of Round 2. The other victory came from Bryan Kim and 
Eric Wu, 7-6 (7-1). 
</P>
