beat Concordia, 4-3, in a Golden State Athletic Conference baseball game 
Tuesday at SCC. 
</P>
<P>
 Ila Borders started for SCC, allowing three runs, two earned, and seven hits 
in six innings.She walked two and didn't have a strikeout. Borders, pitching in 
her first conference game, left with the score tied, 3-3. She threw 78 pitches. 
</P>
<P>
