<P>
 Manufacturer Expands: KCL Projects Ltd., the Anaheim storage-tank maker, is 
expanding to a new building within the city and has signed a $1-million lease 
for a 30,000-square-foot building on two acres in the Orangewood Industrial 
Park. 
</P>
